### @name = Dev
@host = http://localhost:3000
@courseId = cmc1fcqtc003git0v87izokva

### 1. Login (to populate @api_token)
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("api_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 2. List all courses
GET {{host}}/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}

### 3. Get one course by ID
GET {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}

### 4. Create a new course
POST {{host}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}

{
  "title": "New Course Title",
  "description": "A description for the new course"
}

### 5. Update a course
PUT {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 6. Soft-delete a course
DELETE {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}

### 7. Restore a soft-deleted course
PATCH {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{api_token}}